{"tid":2359687,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】太妍驚訝！直播遇到粉絲擔心她變窮：「不要買東西了，留著錢養老啊！」","createTime":"2021-01-09T06:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T09:52:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69a66dbfe7f37e6623ab382998991160e80c977e","tid":2359687,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:05:35.000Z","msg":"這位小粉絲實在是太可愛，太妍震驚的表情真的百看不厭啊XD<br />\n<br />\n近日太妍通過IG直播和粉絲聊天，突然說自己最近有個煩惱，那就是不知道該不該買iPad，問大家：「iPad能做什麼用呢？ 」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太妍接著讀粉絲留言，發現不少人都是勸她不要買，例如：「姐姐，不知道該不該買的時候就應該不買。 」太妍恍然大悟地瞪大眼睛：「啊~是這樣嗎？ 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9e27e25dff21c307c3dbddf3501ef16b/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-08/132877-892473.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9e27e25dff21c307c3dbddf3501ef16b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-08%2F132877-892473.png&h=517fad6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一位粉絲也說：「不知道能做什麼的話就沒有必要買啦。 」太妍覺得意外：「好多人反對我買呢！」<br />\n<br />\n這時太妍讀到一則贊成她買iPad的留言：「可以用來練習《驚人的週六》，應該很需要吧。 」太妍似乎被戳到痛點，皺起眉頭捂著胸口：「啊！好痛。 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3727d1465d31881766a11af90ce8be58/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-08/132877-892474.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3727d1465d31881766a11af90ce8be58%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-08%2F132877-892474.png&h=abb9b534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這時驚人的留言出現了：「姐姐，不要買了，把錢存起來吧，為老后生活著想。 」太妍震驚得一隻眼睛瞪成兩個大，停頓了一秒，連全羅道方言都出來了：「媽耶！」随后忍不住笑出声XD<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c91a23a5a75e68572bf459fc0a5c0a94/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-08/132877-892471.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c91a23a5a75e68572bf459fc0a5c0a94%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-08%2F132877-892471.png&h=c1be954e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要知道，太妍是少女時代的隊長，在韓國一直都是最頂級的愛豆，除了組合活動之外SOLO和廣告也相當活躍，期間賺的錢自不必說，2017年還在故鄉全州買了一座高級商住兩用公寓送給爸媽，當時的售價都超過9億韓元！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cm6WrB3q1pg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dcm6WrB3q1pg&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXSBot4r0pQQ4M2eut5PfJzM%3D&h=ca6bd41f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cm6WrB3q1pg</a>"},{"pid":"7c67d7c8bac4d7508d9300dc6eed96abea108c10","tid":2359687,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:07:41.000Z","msg":"韓國人好有愛❤️"},{"pid":"db8e7384cf9c0cdd0d8f4616b7b2a351656f0f6f","tid":2359687,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:15:15.000Z","msg":"賣自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf5126b3ef2a93689a3dc9db1b3606526e0dabb","tid":2359687,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:17:40.000Z","msg":"「媽耶！」随后忍不住笑出声XD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3835c766aac43acaec0a4017271e1812e1b2e30","tid":2359687,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db8e7384cf9c0cdd0d8f4616b7b2a351656f0f6f","tid":2359687,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:15:15.000Z","msg":"賣自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"唔值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f841099cd76c4418f0bd9ec3f9432065833c745","tid":2359687,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3835c766aac43acaec0a4017271e1812e1b2e30","tid":2359687,"u